        "create_date":"2017-05-08T13:16:00-07:00",
        "description":"<p>Summer Days opens June 2nd! Come and play with the next iteration of Days—\n</p>\n<p>Opening Night: Friday, June 2nd, 6 - 9pm\n</p>\n<p>Join us as we launch Summer Days with ice cream bars and popsicles from Foad Dizadji-Bahmani and cocktails\n</p>\n<p>Opening Weekend: Saturday - Sunday, June 3rd - 4th, 12 - 7pm\n</p>\n<p>Ping Pong Parlor from 5 - 7pm both days\n</p>Ice cream bars and popsicles while supplies last, proceeds benefit <a href=\"http://www.chirla.org/\">CHIRLA</a>\n<p><br>\n</p>",
