        "create_date":"2017-09-30T15:35:00-07:00",
        "description":"<p>Join Days and Corrina Peipon of <a href=\"http://www.pangaeaoutdoorsupply.com/\">Pangaea Outdoor Supply</a> for a Q & A with <a href=\"https://www.courtneycecale.com/\">Courtney Cecale</a>, an anthropologist studying climate change in the high mountains of Peru. An accomplished climber and mountaineer, Cecale documents her work and her travels in stunning photographs that have been published widely, including in National Geographic. We will discuss the joys and challenges of living and working in high alpine conditions in a foreign country.\n</p>",
