        "create_date":"2017-11-22T10:17:00-08:00",
        "description":"<p>Artist Christina Mesiti will be discussing her piece Walk Log—an ongoing walk/motion poem experienced by texting the word \"WALK\" to 323-744-8807.\n</p>\n<p>Join us for a conversation on the practice of walking, the successes and failures of communication, time, motion, aimlessness, art and love.\n</p>",
