        "description":"<p>Join Lenae Day for a festive celebration of the irreverent—an unveiling of cheeky videos for the DAYWEAR line, the new DAYWEAR jingle, and 20% off the collection in anticipation of other Holiday parties!\n</p>\n<p>Expect their awesome wrap pants as well as a preview of new pieces: a jumpsuit, tote, shirt, baby pants, and dog scarf.  Come buy clothes from this local maker!<br>\n</p>\n<p><em>All are welcome: free!</em>\n</p>",
