        "create_date":"2017-12-01T14:41:00-08:00",
        "description":"<p>Are you a member of the Women's Center for Creative Work (WCCW)?\n</p>\n<p>If so, come for the annual Holiday party, this year at Days!\n</p>\n<p>There will be drinks, a White Elephant gift exchange, Face Trace with Jenn Witte, a performance by Girlfriends Touch, a mini FeM Synth Lab setup, and a 15% discount at Days LA for the night! We'll also be selling off the last few copies of our new book, A Feminist Organization's Handbook.\n</p>\n<p>Not a member?  Sign up to support this incredible organization <a href=\"http://womenscenterforcreativework.com/join-us/\">HERE</a>, and come to the party!\n</p>\n<p><em>WCCW Members only</em><em> — </em><a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSeCCzTKe37MSH1YeYbOZITn28CCqljzKIFydwsUZq9hFJ4wLA/viewform\"><em>RSVP HERE</em></a>\n</p>",
