        "_sort_start":1513386000,
        "create_date":"2017-12-01T17:53:00-05:00",
        "description":"<p>Join us for the release of a new book instigated by Litia Perta and designed by Shauna Steinbach. <a href=\"https://www.writingbodies.org/\">Writing Bodies</a> is a constellation of art actions that generates questions, investigations, revelations, risks, fissures, sutures, ruptures, shifts, around the practices, the promises, the politics, of being bodies. The first actions took place at the Elizabeth Foundation for the Arts in New York City from 9 September to 10 October, 2015 and included works by Dylan Mira, Dean Daderko, Jess Arndt, EJ Hill, robbinschilds, Katherine Hubbard, Simone White, Michelle Boulé, and keyon gaskin. This book is the second action.\n</p>\n<p>Drinks by Jess Arndt. Short discussion of the project begins at 6pm.<br>\n</p>\n<p><em>All are welcome: free</em>\n</p>",
        "end":"2017-12-15T23:00:00-05:00",
        "isDraft":false,
