        "_sort_start":1523858400,
        "create_date":"2018-04-09T18:45:00-07:00",
        "description":"Join us Sunday morning at our terrazzo bar for a leisurely browse through the LA & NY Times over coffee and toast.<br>\n<p>We can collectively make analog selections of what's worth reading.\n</p>\n<p><em>All are welcome!</em>\n</p>",
