        "_sort_publish_date":1523986020,
        "_sort_start":1525050000,
        "create_date":"2018-04-17T10:27:00-07:00",
        "description":"<p>We gather to discuss the ideas presented in the Chapters 2 & 3 of City of Quartz by Mike Davis: Power Lines and Homegrown Revolution.\n</p>\n<p><i>Click <a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSchB5KTxylsvEZqWvZOeuKvDSaLMsHfycZQWN8fT8Os8lbzCQ/viewform\">here</a> if you would like to receive more detailed emails about the discussion group!</i>\n</p>",
