        "create_date":"2018-04-30T12:10:00-07:00",
        "description":"<p>We continue to collectively read the NY and LA Times, comparing stories and design over coffee and toast.  Last week we finished the LA Times Crossword: can we complete the NY Times this weekend?\n</p>\n<p>\n\t<i>All are welcome!</i>\n</p>",
