        "description":"<p>We gather to discuss the ideas presented in the Chapters 4 & 5 of City of Quartz by Mike Davis: Fortress LA & The Hammer and the Rock.\n</p>\n<p><i>Click <a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSchB5KTxylsvEZqWvZOeuKvDSaLMsHfycZQWN8fT8Os8lbzCQ/viewform\">here</a> if you would like to receive more detailed emails about the discussion group!</i>\n</p>",
