        "_sort_publish_date":1525397340,
        "_sort_start":1526346000,
        "create_date":"2018-05-03T09:16:00-07:00",
        "description":"<p>Celebrate the miniature! Join us for a presentation and talk from designer Anther Kiley about Cardkits, his line of paper toy kits for adults and children, in-development. The collection is inspired by Anther's childhood \"Fishworld,\" a miniature toy world continuously in construction and reconstruction between 1992 and around 2002.\n</p>\n<p>Refreshments throughout, presentation at 7pm.\n</p>",
