        "_sort_start":1527469200,
        "create_date":"2018-05-23T11:00:00-07:00",
        "description":"<p>We gather to discuss the ideas presented in Chapter 6 of City of Quartz by Mike Davis: New Confessions.\n</p>\n<p>We will be wrapping up the book in two weeks, so if you haven't been coming but would like to participate in the conversation, please join!\n</p>",
