        "_sort_publish_date":1527715260,
        "_sort_start":1528678800,
        "create_date":"2018-05-30T14:21:00-07:00",
        "description":"<p>We are wrapping up our discussion of City of Quartz by Mike Davis! We will cover the last chapter, the prologue from the 2006 edition, and any final thoughts about the whole text.\n</p>\n<p><em>If you haven't been coming but have read the book, please join us for this last meeting!</em>\n</p>",
