        "_sort_publish_date":1529347680,
        "_sort_start":1530597600,
        "create_date":"2018-06-18T11:48:00-07:00",
        "description":"<p>We move from the Rock to Water portions of Cities of Days—from the literal to imagined city; from City of Quartz (Mike Davis) to Invisible Cities (Italo Calvino) and The Book of the City of Ladies (Christine de Pizan); from the physical cities to cities of the mind.\n</p>",
        "end":"2018-07-12T19:00:00-07:00",
