        "create_date":"2018-07-06T08:17:00-07:00",
        "description":"<p>Celebrate the opening of Water!\n</p>\n<p>Drinks, music, and an elemental experience from <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/girlfriendstouch/?hl=en\">Girlfriends' Touch</a>.\n</p>\n<p><em>All are welcome: free!</em>\n</p>",
