        "create_date":"2018-08-24T14:49:00-07:00",
        "description":"<p>Bi-costal <a href=\"https://www.triplemotion.com/\">Triple Motion</a> returns to Cities of Days for a special Water-inspired hand-cranked ice-cream!  One last celebration of Summer before September — come participate in this hand-on experiment of flavors.  Expect something unusual and delicious (seaweed?!).\n</p>\n<p><em>All are welcome!</em>\n</p>",
