        "_sort_publish_date":1539706740,
        "_sort_start":1540144800,
        "create_date":"2018-10-16T09:19:00-07:00",
        "description":"<p>Every Sunday, you're invited to engage in a community gathering around news and crosswords at Days' terrazzo bar.\n</p>\n<p>Coffee, snacks, and the NY Times provide a backdrop for connection and conversation.\n</p>\n<p><em>All are welcome!</em>\n</p>",
