        "create_date":"2018-12-01T18:16:00-08:00",
        "description":"<p>Join us for this live \"cooking show\" with The Wax Apple's Juliana Hung—\n</p>\n<p>Learn the process of cooking this traditional Taiwanese meal at Days' bar, eat a communal meal, & take home your own pickles.\n</p>\n<p><br>\n</p>\n<p>Menu:\n</p>\n<p>Starter— Pickled cucumbers, Pan fried lotus roots\n</p>\n<p>Main— Minced Pork with shiitake mushrooms over rice. Garnished with green onions and pickled Daikon.\n</p>\n<p>Dessert—Red bean infused jello with shaved ice\n</p>\n<p>Drinks—Taiwan beer\n</p>\n<p>Gift—Pair of Hinoki Chopsticks, Pickles (bring a jar!)\n</p>\n<p><br>\n</p>\n<p><em>Limited to 10 people—</em>\n</p>\n<p><em>$30 - book your ticket <a href=\"https://days-la.myshopify.com/products/wax-apple-cooking-show-dinner?variant=21210069794876\">here</a>!</em>\n</p>",
