        "description":"<p>The week before Christmas we will be open everyday! Come shop!<br><br>\n</p>\n<p>Holiday Hours:\n</p>\n<p>Monday - Wednesday December 17th - 19th\n</p>\n<p>2 - 7pm\n</p>\n<p>Thursday - Sunday December 20th - 23rd\n</p>\n<p>11 - 7pm\n</p>",
