        "create_date":"2018-12-10T16:55:00-08:00",
        "description":"<p>Join us for the second round of this live \"cooking show\" with The Wax Apple's Juliana Hung—\n</p>\n<p>Learn the process of cooking a traditional Taiwanese meal at Days' bar, eat a communal meal, & take home your own pickles.<br>\n</p>\n<p><strong>Menu:</strong>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p1\">Starter—pickled celery, marinated woods ear, popcorn chicken with fried basil\n</p>\n<p class=\"p1\">Main—pork rib soup with dates, tossed noodles infused with scallion, ginger, oil, soy dressing and topped with sesame oil\n</p>\n<p class=\"p1\">Dessert—grass jelly with sweet ginger syrup\n</p>\n<p class=\"p1\">Drinks—Taiwan beer, Oolong tea\n</p>\n<p class=\"p1\"><br>\n</p>\n<p><em>Limited to 8 people—</em>\n</p>\n<p><em>$30 - book your ticket <a href=\"https://days-la.myshopify.com/products/wax-apple-cooking-show-dinner?variant=21210069794876\">here</a>!</em>\n</p>",
